						               													<description>Farmatropic is a deck-building farm-building game with a colourful tropical theme. An upcoming game from Team Custard Kraken coming to Kickstarter in 2020 and releasing 2021.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Farmatropic you build your farm field by field and barn by barn in front of you on the table whilst filling your deck with actions allowing for increased efficiency. You use these farm and barn spaces to grow crops and raise animals using a turn-card method to track plant growth and live-stock progress. There a numerous cards you can acquire that permanently affix to farms and barns to increase defences against other players Shenanigans.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players must manage their farm on the table in front you while also balancing their decks with on-board cards, in hand defences, crops, animals and currency.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is the player to acquire the highest value of wealth by the time either the farm card or barn card decks are exhausted.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
